s the fully\nrandom model despite the greatly reduced degree of independent randomness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2010 13:30:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Mar 2010 16:29:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2012 12:44:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 3 Oct 2012 12:08:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-21"}
